
                      Dahsee -- A D-Bus monnitoring tool.
                       http://github.com/ambrevar/dahsee

             Copyright 2012 Pierre Neidhardt <ambrevar@gmail.com>

Configuration
-------------

The only required dependency is D-Bus. You will need it for compilation.

Building
--------

  $ make

Installation
------------

  $ make install

Manuals
-------

  $ man dahsee


Git Repository
--------------

gitweb: http://github.com/ambrevar/dahsee


Hacking
-------

Dahsee uses the Linux kernel coding style, with 4-spaces tabs.
